<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about nodejs)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/nodejs.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Aug 2017 19:45:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>EPROTO: protocol error, symlink '../acorn/bin/acorn' -&gt; '/usr/development/mint-ui-starter-master/node_modules/.bin/acorn'</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/eproto-protocol-error-symlink-acornbinacorn-usrdevelopmentmint-ui-starter-masternode_modulesbinacorn/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;方法1：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; npm install --no-bin-links
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;方法1可能会导致后续过程缺少依赖。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;方法2：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
使用管理员权限打开docker。
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>javascript</category><category>nodejs</category><category>npm</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/eproto-protocol-error-symlink-acornbinacorn-usrdevelopmentmint-ui-starter-masternode_modulesbinacorn/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 04 Apr 2017 11:17:19 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>openSUSE安装nodejs</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/opensusean-zhuang-nodejs/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;1、下载源码。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v6.10.1/node-v6.10.1-linux-x64.tar.gz
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、解压。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; tar zxvf node-v6.10.1-linux-x64.tar.gz
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、链接命令。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo ln -s /home/long/software/node/bin/node /usr/local/bin/node
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo ln -s /home/long/software/node/bin/npm /usr/local/bin/npm
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; long@linux-iyb2:~&amp;gt; node -v
v6.10.1
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; long@linux-iyb2:~&amp;gt; npm -v
3.10.10
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>nodejs</category><category>openSUSE</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/opensusean-zhuang-nodejs/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 28 Mar 2017 00:58:42 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>